                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320517-290-off1638 t18320517-290-crimeloc1640"></join>, putting her in fear, and taking from her person, and against her will, 1 shawl, value 5s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18320517-290-victim2079" type="victimName">
                        Michael 
                        Brennan
                     <interp inst="t18320517-290-victim2079" type="surname" value="Brennan"></interp>
